### 차량 등록
POST http://localhost:8080/api/vehicles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleNumber": "12가3456",
  "vehicleModel": "Hyundai Staria",
  "fuelType": "DIESEL",
  "averageFuelEfficiency": 11.8,
  "vehicleStatus": "AVAILABLE",
  "remark": "본사 차량"
}

###

### 전체 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/vehicles

###

### 단건 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/api/vehicles/1

###

### 수정
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/vehicles/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "vehicleNumber": "12가3456",
  "vehicleModel": "Hyundai Staria Lounge",
  "fuelType": "DIESEL",
  "averageFuelEfficiency": 12.4,
  "vehicleStatus": "AVAILABLE",
  "remark": "정상 운행"
}

###

### 삭제
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/vehicles/1